{"tid":1459512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Whatsapp宣傳","createTime":"2019-08-12T17:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T17:10:50.000Z","uid":62032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be55199de2d03353cc8d269c84ffe82ae18a6574","tid":1459512,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:47:46.000Z","msg":"就算大家嘅親朋戚友同事藍絲<br />\n有幾咁鍾意用微信嗰咋大陸app<br />\n但<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">喺香港點都會有個WhatsApp</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解唔<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放啲真相圖去Whatsapp&rdquo;動態&rdquo;</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與其去Facebook滲透啲假account<br />\n不如試吓<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由自己身邊嘅人着手</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n放上動態就<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">等於貼街招</span></span><br />\n佢可能齋睇㗎咋<br />\n但起碼佢會睇到多啲野<br />\n你又可以等人主動搵你<br />\n重點係<br />\n因為佢同你係認識嘅 又冇好似fb咁有假ac照住<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢要顧自己形象<br />\n會少啲講乜嘢&rdquo;打死晒佢就啱啦&rdquo;呢啲垃圾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n又由於你冇係gp倒講<br />\n就算有人放上gp講<br />\n你都唔係挑起事端嘅人<br />\n你大可以好委屈咁<br />\n用返佢哋啲邏輯<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&ldquo;你嘅言論自由就係自由，<br />\n我嘅言論自由就唔係自由咩？<br />\n我分享喺自己個動態都唔可以？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n但要做嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前提係<br />\n你需要有被討厭嘅勇氣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你要預咗有人會搵你嘈<br />\n你要預咗佢問你證據，而你要做定資料蒐集fact check<br />\n<br />\n但本小利大<br />\n點解唔做埋？？<br />\n佢哋到時分享畀啲朋友<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">效果絕對大過你放上Fb好多倍</span></span>"},{"pid":"2d184422c8fc132082e154125fb162d26eee7d0c","tid":1459512,"uid":257394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:50:36.000Z","msg":"因為whatsapp動態無人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89c6e8b660de9a4cb8f6f5e95148b7837e2fb3c","tid":1459512,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d184422c8fc132082e154125fb162d26eee7d0c","tid":1459512,"uid":257394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:50:36.000Z","msg":"因為whatsapp動態無人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:54:33.000Z","msg":"就係見少人用開<br />\n咁咪正正係任你寫嘅白板囉<br />\n我哋就係要開墾呢塊土地<br />\n<br />\n咁開課嘅前提就係你要令你屋企人知道有嘢睇<br />\n你一開頭可以放啲普通嘢出嚟先<br />\n之後先至入正題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61981940c799512c9307b2a3b734b938119780bd","tid":1459512,"uid":36089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:55:23.000Z","msg":"求求大家，盡快去換美元現鈔！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f3276aad7033aae8517e3b52f2ee656d4fc7edfc","tid":1459512,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d184422c8fc132082e154125fb162d26eee7d0c","tid":1459512,"uid":257394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:50:36.000Z","msg":"因為whatsapp動態無人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"我呢幾星期都有用<br />\n發現原來係會有人睇<br />\n有啲人睇完係會搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e3a616a31aa6b0c1a03dd316bc93fabd9fed76","tid":1459512,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cla